---
import { pageTitle } from '../../config/site';
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout
	title={pageTitle('FAQ')}
	description="Frequently asked questions about boat tours from Split, Blue Cave visits, weather, and safety."
>
	<main id="main" class="main">
		<h1 class="title">Frequently asked questions</h1>
		<p class="intro">
			General guest questions below — a separate <strong>FAQ — SEAYOU</strong>-style block appears on the board for
			channel-specific copy; we can swap in partner wording when final.
		</p>

		<section class="section" aria-labelledby="g-heading">
			<h2 id="g-heading" class="h2">General</h2>
			<dl class="faq">
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Is the Blue Cave ticket included?</dt>
					<dd>
						Cave entry is often billed separately on-site and depends on sea conditions and official opening hours. We
						show what’s included before you pay.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>What if the weather is bad?</dt>
					<dd>
						We monitor forecasts. Routes may be shortened, reordered, or rescheduled so the day stays safe and enjoyable.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Private vs group tours?</dt>
					<dd>
						Group tours follow a fixed timetable; private charters pick timing and pacing within operational limits — see
						<a href="/tours/create-perfect-day-private">Create your perfect day at sea</a>.
					</dd>
				</div>
				<div class="faq__row">
					<dt>Where do we meet?</dt>
					<dd>
						Split’s Riva — stand 14. You’ll get the exact pin and time after booking (FigJam sticky: “Meeting point:
						Adresa”).
					</dd>
				</div>
			</dl>
		</section>

		<section class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="s-heading">
			<h2 id="s-heading" class="h2">FAQ — SEAYOU (placeholder)</h2>
			<p class="muted">
				Reserve this block for partner-specific cancellation terms, voucher redemption, or OTA handoff — content TBD with
				stakeholders.
			</p>
			<ul class="bullet">
				<li>Redemption windows and ID requirements</li>
				<li>How to change a reservation made through a partner</li>
				<li>Language of operation on board</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	.main {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 4rem;
	}

	.title {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
		color: var(--color-nav);
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.intro {
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.section--alt {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: #f8fafc;
		border-radius: var(--radius);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-nav);
	}

	.faq__row {
		padding: 1rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.faq__row:first-of-type {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	dt {
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-nav);
		margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
	}

	dd {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.muted {
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.bullet {
		margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}
</style>
